name: Eleven (itch) (Neuropanda)
description:
A short runner with a bifurcation mechanic about number 11. Press Enter once to turn into two units, and twice to return to eleven.

Features:

  •     3 locations
  •     4 unique obstacle
  •   ~ 30 minutes of gameplay

Control:

  • A, D - move
  • Enter - bifurcation
